---
title: Carb Smart Creamy Double Bacon-Cauliflower Chowder with Cheddar Cheese and Chives
description: This luscious, creamy chowder gets its depth from nutty-sweet roasted cauliflower and salty bacon fat. Extra crunch from the seeds and bacon bits on top make this an unforgettable bowl of goodness!

